	abstract = {Hongmei He (Intelligent System Lab, University of Bristol): Soft Computing Approaches Under the Framework of Hierarchical Decision Making or Classification System With the development of AI, we can see there are a surprising number of the brain functions of the human Intelligent System (IS) are quite similar to those of an artificial IS, since most artificial ISs are modelled through naturally emulating human intelligence. A wide variety of approaches have been utilised in the functional design of artificial ISs. For example, fuzzy logic for robustness, decision trees for the transparency of reasoning, machine learning for knowledge learning, semantics for understandability, probabilistic reasoning, and neural computing, etc.},
